@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_icetxh(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = ((wp.abs(v0 + 0.06) * wp.abs(v0 + 0.34)) / 0.94)
    v0 = wp.exp(((v1 + 0.80 - tmp + 0.09) - 0.95))
    v2 = v1
    v2 = (0.44 + ((v1 + 0.87 + v2 + 0.18) / (v2 + 0.30 + v0 + 0.94)))
    tmp = wp.sin((0.57 * tmp))
    v0 = wp.sin(((v0 + 0.03 - v0 + 0.71) / (tmp + 0.12 * v2 + 0.25)))
    data[tid] = v0
